.441" end="1:10.195">ting</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">等待着满怀爱意的一瞥</span></p><p begin="1:11.103" end="1:17.755" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.103" end="1:13.070">Oh,</span> <span begin="1:13.070" end="1:13.277">a</span> <span begin="1:13.277" end="1:13.529">ne</span><span begin="1:13.529" end="1:13.750">ver</span><span begin="1:13.750" end="1:13.961">en</span><span begin="1:13.961" end="1:14.430">ding</span> <span begin="1:14.430" end="1:14.785">hope</span> <span begin="1:14.785" end="1:15.231">to</span> <span begin="1:15.231" end="1:15.699">men</span><span begin="1:15.699" end="1:16.143">d it</span> <span begin="1:16.143" end="1:17.755">all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无止境的希望能治愈一切</span></p><p begin="1:18.170" end="1:24.771" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:18.170" end="1:20.176">Flow,</span> <span begin="1:20.176" end="1:20.414">le</span><span begin="1:20.414" end="1:20.562">t our</span> <span begin="1:20.562" end="1:20.777">time</span> <span begin="1:20.777" end="1:21.019">re</span><span begin="1:21.019" end="1:21.307">main</span> <span begin="1:21.307" end="1:21.438">and</span> <span begin="1:21.438" end="1:21.826">wait</span> <span begin="1:21.826" end="1:22.331">for</span> <span begin="1:22.331" end="1:22.758">voids</span> <span begin="1:22.758" end="1:23.168">to</span> <span begin="1:23.168" end="1:24.771">fall</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">起起落落 就让时间停留于此 等待空寂降临</span></p><p begin="1:25.038" end="1:27.902" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:25.038" end="1:25.232">As</span><span begin="1:25.232" end="1:25.667">cen</span><span begin="1:25.667" end="1:25.883">ding</span> <span begin="1:25.883" end="1:26.599">through</span> <span begin="1:26.599" end="1:26.790">the</span> <span begin="1:26.790" end="1:27.172">mo</span><span begin="1:27.172" end="1:27.902">tions</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">于一切生机中蜿蜒而上</span></p><p begin="1: